  "bodyText": "Free workshops on taxes, social security and managing your money, delivered with partners like the BRA, NISSS, Sagicor and BPWCCUL.\n\n## Overview\n\nEducation and assistance with tax, NIS/social security, and financial services. Partners: Barbados Revenue Authority, NISSS, Sagicor, BPWCCUL.\n\n## Who can apply\n\n- 18+ years\n- Interest in finance, tax, education\n\n## How to apply\n\nComplete the short application form to register your interest. Your progress is saved automatically.\n\n<!-- [Apply now](https://alpha.gov.bb/youth-and-community/children-families-community/ceep/form) -->\n\n## More information\n\n[Go to the official site for Community Engagement and Educational Programme (CEEP)](https://comdev.gov.bb/registration-ceep/)"
